      <title>泽连斯基抵达冰岛会见北欧领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/zelenskiy-arrives-in-iceland-to-meet-with-nordic-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基周一前往冰岛与北欧领导人举行会晤，寻求获得该国战争目标的支持。]]></description>
