    <item>
      <title>标准首席执行官称评级偏见给非洲造成数十亿美元的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ratings-bias-costs-africa-billions-of-dollars-standard-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲最大银行的行长表示，由于信用评级公司对风险的认知过高，非洲国家面临更高的融资成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ratings-bias-costs-africa-billions-of-dollars-standard-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 13:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默在决定英国成败的预算案前向批评者发起挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/starmer-challenges-his-critics-ahead-of-make-or-break-uk-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默表示，工党政府别无选择，只能在周三的预算中提出不受欢迎的增税和削减开支的政策，并将英国公共财政困境直接归咎于其保守党前任，并要求他们解释他们将采取哪些不同的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/starmer-challenges-his-critics-ahead-of-make-or-break-uk-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯计划举办“自由”集会，特朗普向男性施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-plans-freedom-rally-trump-courts-men-in-final-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统竞选活动进入最后一周，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯和前总统唐纳德·特朗普陷入了激烈的竞争，他们采取了截然不同的宣传策略来激励支持者并赢得剩下的少数可说服选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-plans-freedom-rally-trump-courts-men-in-final-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>臭名昭著的犯罪头目成为印度-加拿大争端的关键人物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/infamous-crime-boss-becomes-pivotal-figure-in-india-canada-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于锡克教分离主义领袖遇刺事件导致印度和加拿大外交关系紧张，人们的注意力现在转向印度最臭名昭著的黑帮之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/infamous-crime-boss-becomes-pivotal-figure-in-india-canada-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平呼吁中国寻找更多方式展现软实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/xi-calls-on-china-to-find-more-ways-to-project-soft-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平呼吁中国展现更多软实力，强调他要增强中国在全球的影响力并挑战美国主导的秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/xi-calls-on-china-to-find-more-ways-to-project-soft-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:32:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多竞争对手承诺取消许多新建住宅的联邦销售税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 表示，如果他当选总理，他将取消加拿大针对售价低于 100 万加元（719,700 美元）的新房征收的 5% 的全国销售税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对党领袖警告新一轮选举抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/mozambique-eelctions-opposition-leader-warns-of-renewed-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 是一位激进的反对派总统候选人，他在 10 月 9 日举行的莫桑比克大选中获得亚军，他警告称，将会有更多人抗议他所说的欺诈性选举结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/mozambique-eelctions-opposition-leader-warns-of-renewed-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友在朝鲜驻军问题上面临有限选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ukraine-allies-face-limited-options-as-north-korea-troops-arrive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯决定派遣朝鲜军队来增强其厌战的军队，这让乌克兰的盟友意识到，如果不进一步升级冲突，他们几乎没有其他应对措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ukraine-allies-face-limited-options-as-north-korea-troops-arrive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利中右翼反对党在地方选举中取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/chile-s-center-right-opposition-gains-ground-in-local-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利传统的中右翼政党在周末的地方选举中赢得了几个关键的席位，在选民重返投票站选举下一任总统的一年之前，他们在反对派中占据上风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/chile-s-center-right-opposition-gains-ground-in-local-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 03:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
